<div style="border:solid 1px #000000; color:#4e00ad; border-radius: 10px; background:#e3ddeb; padding:5px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding:10px">
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><strong><em>Now my fear of falling,</em></strong><br />
<strong><em>Is nowhere in me calling,</em></strong><br />
<strong><em>Telling me to run while I still can.</em></strong><br />
<strong><em>Holding nothing back now,</em></strong><br />
<strong><em>Seems I have at last found,</em></strong><br />
<strong><em>Love that makes me want to give you all I am.</em></strong></p>
</div>
<br />
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p>-Katherine Jenkins - <em>Fear Of Falling</em></p>
</div>
</div>
<p>This would not have happened if not for the love, support, and gentle prodding by my lovely boy. Thank you, Fox. I love you.</p>
<p>My critters were <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/plaidypus" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4187161); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4187161&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1598904733" alt="plaidypus" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4187161)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/plaidypus" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4187161); return false;">plaidypus</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/luxaiko" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5963620); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5963620&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1598904733" alt="Luxaiko" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5963620)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/luxaiko" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5963620); return false;">Luxaiko</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rockteethmotheyes" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4022320); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4022320&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1598904733" alt="RockTeethMothEyes" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4022320)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rockteethmotheyes" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4022320); return false;">RockTeethMothEyes</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5255688); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5255688&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1598904733" alt="DrAkimoto" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5255688)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5255688); return false;">DrAkimoto</a></span>. Thank you too, 'cause y'all rock ass.</p>
<p>Finally, if you liked this and you'd like to read more of my work, please visit <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/malycegraves-author">my author page!</a></p>

